1
00:00:36,995 --> 00:00:42,125
<i>Looks like him and Alex</i>
<i>are agents working against us.</i>

2
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:50,258
<i>And when that happens</i>

3
00:00:50,341 --> 00:00:52,927
Mikoy will be dead.

4
00:00:53,762 --> 00:00:54,971
Why are you calling?

5
00:00:55,055 --> 00:00:58,349
<i>Didn't you say</i>
<i>I shouldn't answer this phone?</i>

6
00:00:58,433 --> 00:01:00,935
This is urgent and I need
to talk to you right away.

7
00:01:01,519 --> 00:01:03,229
Why? What's wrong?

8
00:01:03,313 --> 00:01:05,148
Mikoy, listen to me carefully.

9
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:06,691
You need to stay away from Chiara.

10
00:01:19,496 --> 00:01:21,331
And what they're planning to do next.

11
00:01:23,333 --> 00:01:25,001
<i>No, you're wrong.</i>

12
00:01:25,084 --> 00:01:27,212
Okay. What you're saying is impossible.

13
00:01:27,295 --> 00:01:29,005
Because Chiara is in Prague.

14
00:01:29,088 --> 00:01:30,381
<i>I knew you'd say that.</i>

15
00:01:30,465 --> 00:01:33,426
<i>But it's better if we meet in person</i>
<i>and I'll explain everything there.</i>

16
00:01:34,010 --> 00:01:35,637
But for now, I need
to secure your safety first.

17
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,555
Because she might already be
making a move against you.

18
00:01:38,056 --> 00:01:39,265
I'll message you the location.

19
00:02:19,889 --> 00:02:22,433
Mikoy, What's wrong?

20
00:02:22,517 --> 00:02:24,060
Why are you reacting like that?

21
00:02:24,144 --> 00:02:25,979
I need to meet with Alex.

22
00:02:26,062 --> 00:02:27,272
I'll come with you.

23
00:02:27,355 --> 00:02:28,690
I'm coming too.

24
00:02:28,773 --> 00:02:30,233
No, stay here.

25
00:02:30,316 --> 00:02:32,235
I'm going alone.

26
00:02:32,318 --> 00:02:34,070
What are you talking about?

27
00:02:34,154 --> 00:02:36,698
I'm coming with you
whether you like it or not.

28
00:02:36,781 --> 00:02:37,615
Dad.

29
00:02:37,699 --> 00:02:38,825
No.

30
00:02:40,493 --> 00:02:43,705
I know I've said things
you weren't supposed to know.

31
00:02:43,788 --> 00:02:46,541
But that doesn't mean
you have to get involved in this.

32
00:02:47,292 --> 00:02:49,210
Dad, you can't get dragged into this.

33
00:02:50,086 --> 00:02:51,796
So please, just let me handle it.

34
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,423
This is my fight.

35
00:02:56,551 --> 00:02:58,928
Mikoy. This isn't just your fight.

36
00:03:00,471 --> 00:03:01,598
You're a Pinagpala.

37
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,683
We're all Pinagpala.

38
00:03:03,766 --> 00:03:05,435
This is our fight.

39
00:03:15,486 --> 00:03:17,030
But not this time.

40
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:20,867
I won't allow my son
to put himself in danger.

41
00:03:22,744 --> 00:03:23,620
Dad.

42
00:03:24,621 --> 00:03:26,706
It was my decision to get
involved in this mess.

43
00:03:27,332 --> 00:03:31,377
So please trust me
that I can stand by this decision.

44
00:03:32,754 --> 00:03:34,130
And besides, Mom.

45
00:03:35,173 --> 00:03:37,091
She has no idea what's going on.

46
00:03:38,426 --> 00:03:40,303
Dad, we need to protect her.

47
00:03:40,386 --> 00:03:42,931
And if something bad happens to me.

48
00:03:43,014 --> 00:03:45,183
At least I know both of you
will be there for her.

49
00:03:50,939 --> 00:03:52,523
Dad, Mom needs you.

50
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:06,204
Sianong!

51
00:04:07,705 --> 00:04:08,623
Sofie.

52
00:04:09,707 --> 00:04:11,084
What is really going on?

53
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:17,715
There was another attempt on your dad.

54
00:04:17,799 --> 00:04:18,883
What?

55
00:04:19,509 --> 00:04:21,177
Where is he? Is he okay?

56
00:04:24,389 --> 00:04:27,350
Don't worry, he was just
talking to Alex earlier.

57
00:04:27,433 --> 00:04:28,935
And trust your dad.

58
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,436
He's sharp.

59
00:04:34,107 --> 00:04:35,108
Sofie.

60
00:04:44,158 --> 00:04:45,493
I'm sorry.

61
00:04:45,576 --> 00:04:46,911
Does it hurt?

62
00:04:46,995 --> 00:04:49,330
Yes, when you hit me.

63
00:04:49,414 --> 00:04:51,916
- It's nothing.
- Dad…

64
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:55,211
It's far from the intestines, come on.
Stop crying already.

65
00:04:55,295 --> 00:04:57,922
- It's always "far from the intestines."
- I'm fine.

66
00:04:58,006 --> 00:04:59,299
I know you.

67
00:04:59,382 --> 00:05:02,885
Look at this, it's just like an ant bite.

68
00:05:02,969 --> 00:05:04,137
It's nothing.

69
00:05:07,223 --> 00:05:08,683
It hurts!

70
00:05:11,728 --> 00:05:14,605
It's okay. That's enough, stop crying.

71
00:05:14,689 --> 00:05:16,899
- Come on.
- It's always "okay."

72
00:05:16,983 --> 00:05:18,985
I'm okay now, okay?

73
00:05:19,068 --> 00:05:20,862
- Are you sure?
- Yes, I'm okay.

74
00:05:20,945 --> 00:05:22,113
Sir.

75
00:05:22,196 --> 00:05:24,866
Is Alex not with you?

76
00:05:27,118 --> 00:05:28,494
Angelito.

77
00:05:28,578 --> 00:05:30,371
Whatever you know right now.

78
00:05:30,455 --> 00:05:32,373
No one else should know about it.

79
00:05:33,333 --> 00:05:35,668
- Is that clear?
- Yes, sir.

80
00:05:36,169 --> 00:05:40,298
Because this is the best way
to protect your brother.

81
00:05:40,381 --> 00:05:43,176
By keeping these secrets hidden.

82
00:05:43,259 --> 00:05:44,677
I understand, Dad.

83
00:05:44,761 --> 00:05:47,680
No one should know, not even your mother.

84
00:05:47,764 --> 00:05:49,557
You mean to say…

85
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:52,143
- I'll lie to Mom?
- You're not going to lie.

86
00:05:52,852 --> 00:05:56,314
There are just things you don't say
or tell her.

87
00:05:56,981 --> 00:05:58,066
Okay.

88
00:05:58,149 --> 00:06:03,529
And this is also the best way
for you to protect yourself.

89
00:06:04,113 --> 00:06:06,407
If someone finds out
that you know the truth.

90
00:06:08,993 --> 00:06:10,536
Believe it or not.

91
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:13,331
Many people want the truth dead.

92
00:06:27,178 --> 00:06:28,096
Kian.

93
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:33,267
Bro.

94
00:06:34,977 --> 00:06:36,646
Do you know where Alex is?

95
00:06:36,729 --> 00:06:38,231
I didn't notice.

96
00:06:41,234 --> 00:06:42,068
Mikoy might…

97
00:06:47,782 --> 00:06:48,658
Hey.

98
00:06:51,327 --> 00:06:53,162
Alex sent her here.

99
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:13,975
<i>Sir, the agent escaped from us.</i>

100
00:07:14,058 --> 00:07:15,601
Idiots!

101
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:20,231
The task I gave you was so simple.

102
00:07:23,359 --> 00:07:24,694
But we'll still look for her.

103
00:07:42,211 --> 00:07:43,254
Viktor.

104
00:07:43,754 --> 00:07:46,048
If things are already this messy
here in the Philippines

105
00:07:46,132 --> 00:07:47,633
let's go back to Prague.

106
00:07:47,717 --> 00:07:49,510
It's still our home, right?

107
00:08:18,706 --> 00:08:20,958
Thank you for all your help.

108
00:08:23,503 --> 00:08:25,838
If you still need anything.

109
00:08:25,922 --> 00:08:27,632
Just let me know.

110
00:08:40,102 --> 00:08:42,104
You're not the one who hurt me.

111
00:08:53,491 --> 00:08:56,702
Because I let myself
drown in this illusion.

112
00:09:01,415 --> 00:09:03,501
I lost touch with reality.

113
00:09:10,049 --> 00:09:12,343
I learned the hard way.

114
00:09:31,571 --> 00:09:32,863
What's your plan?

115
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:41,581
I will make sure.

116
00:09:41,664 --> 00:09:45,042
Everyone who betrayed me will pay!

117
00:10:30,004 --> 00:10:32,673
Where are you? Are you home?

118
00:10:33,424 --> 00:10:35,926
No, what about you? Are you still out?

119
00:10:42,975 --> 00:10:44,727
She said I've been gone for too long.

120
00:10:45,394 --> 00:10:46,312
What about you?

121
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:49,690
Sounds like you're out too.

122
00:10:49,774 --> 00:10:52,360
Yes. I'm at a restaurant right now.

123
00:10:52,443 --> 00:10:54,695
<i>It's too quiet at home so,</i>

124
00:10:54,779 --> 00:10:56,656
I had to go out.

125
00:10:57,406 --> 00:10:58,616
It depresses me there.

126
00:10:58,699 --> 00:11:00,868
Don't worry.

127
00:11:02,119 --> 00:11:03,663
When I get home.

128
00:11:04,455 --> 00:11:07,083
I'll cook for you again.

129
00:11:08,626 --> 00:11:12,922
The kind of food you'll never forget.

130
00:11:13,005 --> 00:11:15,508
Wow, I miss that already.

131
00:11:16,425 --> 00:11:18,427
<i>I miss your cooking, sweetheart.</i>

132
00:11:26,102 --> 00:11:27,603
Since you’re not here.

133
00:11:35,778 --> 00:11:37,154
I hope I can see you soon too.

134
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:50,876
Who were you talking to?

135
00:11:53,003 --> 00:11:53,963
Chiara.

136
00:11:54,505 --> 00:11:55,881
And she's in Prague.

137
00:11:56,424 --> 00:11:58,217
So what you're saying is impossible.

138
00:12:01,011 --> 00:12:03,597
She was at Sir Norberto's house earlier.

139
00:12:20,865 --> 00:12:23,075
How are you so sure it was Chiara?

140
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:24,368
Do you have evidence?

141
00:12:24,452 --> 00:12:26,495
We are still processing the scene.

142
00:12:27,955 --> 00:12:29,915
So we have forensic traces of her.

143
00:12:35,754 --> 00:12:37,131
No, that's impossible.

144
00:12:37,214 --> 00:12:38,507
She could never do that.

145
00:12:38,591 --> 00:12:39,717
Really?

146
00:12:40,676 --> 00:12:42,678
You actually believe what you're saying?

147
00:12:42,761 --> 00:12:44,388
Zero possibility

148
00:12:44,472 --> 00:12:47,266
that Chiara is capable of being
La Fornarina?

149
00:12:48,684 --> 00:12:51,103
Like some innocent little saint?

150
00:12:52,229 --> 00:12:53,898
Unlike you, I'm not blind.

151
00:12:53,981 --> 00:12:57,359
I'm not blind to what I feel for her.

152
00:12:59,862 --> 00:13:03,324
And I can clearly see
what kind of person she is.

153
00:13:05,659 --> 00:13:06,869
It's not easy to see.

154
00:13:06,952 --> 00:13:08,621
It's not easy to notice.

155
00:13:08,704 --> 00:13:11,540
Because she's good at hiding
who she really is.

156
00:13:12,249 --> 00:13:13,834
But no matter what she does.

157
00:13:13,918 --> 00:13:16,921
The stench of what she's hiding
will eventually come out.

158
00:13:17,004 --> 00:13:18,672
And that's her true nature.

159
00:13:20,549 --> 00:13:23,135
Can you really say that you know Chiara?

160
00:13:34,396 --> 00:13:37,066
I know this is shocking
and hard to believe.

161
00:13:37,149 --> 00:13:38,984
But this isn't just suspicion, Mikoy.

162
00:13:39,068 --> 00:13:41,028
Carlota already confirmed it.

163
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:46,158
The same Carlota, the secretary
Viktor planted around you.

164
00:13:47,117 --> 00:13:49,286
The secretary you thought was the enemy.

165
00:13:49,370 --> 00:13:53,082
The same secretary we initially
suspected to be La Fornarina.

166
00:13:54,083 --> 00:13:55,709
She is not La Fornarina.

167
00:13:58,796 --> 00:14:01,090
And now she's our state witness.

168
00:14:01,173 --> 00:14:03,300
And now she's on our side.

169
00:14:23,779 --> 00:14:25,698
Stop closing your eyes to it.

170
00:14:27,908 --> 00:14:30,995
The most dangerous Moraviano
is already right in front of you.

171
00:14:53,559 --> 00:14:55,394
Open your eyes to the truth

172
00:14:55,477 --> 00:14:59,189
that the biggest enemy here
is the person you love.

173
00:14:59,773 --> 00:15:00,774
That's enough.

174
00:15:01,984 --> 00:15:02,985
Mikoy.

175
00:15:03,068 --> 00:15:04,653
I said that's enough!

176
00:15:05,863 --> 00:15:06,780
Mikoy!

177
00:15:10,868 --> 00:15:11,702
Mikoy.

178
00:15:12,953 --> 00:15:14,121
Mikoy.

179
00:15:14,204 --> 00:15:15,789
Don't be stupid.

180
00:15:17,249 --> 00:15:19,668
The first time I saw you
you were the one who said

181
00:15:19,752 --> 00:15:21,462
never to underestimate you.

182
00:15:21,545 --> 00:15:24,715
People shouldn’t treat you as dumb
for not finishing school.

183
00:15:25,257 --> 00:15:26,884
And I believed you.

184
00:15:26,967 --> 00:15:28,802
In the short time I've known you,

185
00:15:28,886 --> 00:15:31,472
I've come to realize how smart you are.

186
00:15:31,555 --> 00:15:34,058
Mikoy, I know you're intelligent.

187
00:15:34,141 --> 00:15:37,353
And I know your heart already knows
what the truth really is.

188
00:15:42,691 --> 00:15:45,527
That you've made the biggest
mistake of loving someone

189
00:15:45,611 --> 00:15:47,071
who doesn't deserve to be loved.

190
00:15:47,154 --> 00:15:48,822
And what do you know about love?

191
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:50,366
About us?

192
00:15:52,284 --> 00:15:53,869
You know, Chiara was right.

193
00:15:54,954 --> 00:15:56,622
I really should be careful around you.

194
00:15:56,705 --> 00:15:58,958
Are you really that shallow, Alex?

195
00:16:00,668 --> 00:16:04,004
You're doing all of this
just to break us apart?

196
00:16:04,964 --> 00:16:06,298
Just because you like me?

197
00:16:10,594 --> 00:16:11,971
What are you talking about?

198
00:16:17,726 --> 00:16:19,019
We're done.

199
00:16:43,877 --> 00:16:47,339
You know, being a state witness

200
00:16:47,423 --> 00:16:49,425
is a long process.

201
00:16:50,801 --> 00:16:55,055
Because first we need to verify all the
information you're giving us.

202
00:16:55,139 --> 00:16:58,726
It has to be verified,
the sources have to be reliable.

203
00:16:58,809 --> 00:16:59,893
Okay?

204
00:16:59,977 --> 00:17:02,855
It can't be that
you just keep talking nonstop,

205
00:17:02,938 --> 00:17:05,107
keep spilling stories and then we

206
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:09,069
just nod along to everything you feed us.

207
00:17:13,949 --> 00:17:15,659
You still have a long way to go.

208
00:17:16,243 --> 00:17:18,912
But for the meantime

209
00:17:19,496 --> 00:17:22,458
we'll transfer you first to one
of our safe houses.

210
00:17:22,541 --> 00:17:24,626
You know, for safety.

211
00:17:27,337 --> 00:17:30,257
Cutie, you know…

212
00:17:30,924 --> 00:17:32,760
You're hard to read too.

213
00:17:44,813 --> 00:17:46,648
You like Agent Alex, don't you?

214
00:17:53,322 --> 00:17:55,282
Okay, believe it or not.

215
00:17:55,365 --> 00:17:59,203
The relationship Alex and I have
it's purely professional.

216
00:17:59,787 --> 00:18:02,456
Sure. That's a lot of talking.

217
00:18:02,539 --> 00:18:05,959
Got it already
and yet you still keep explaining.

218
00:18:08,587 --> 00:18:12,257
I hope you're the one
assigned to guard me.

219
00:18:12,841 --> 00:18:17,888
You know, my bodyguard at the safe house.

220
00:18:17,971 --> 00:18:19,765
You know what I hope?

221
00:18:27,397 --> 00:18:29,608
Especially the innocent
people getting dragged in

222
00:18:29,691 --> 00:18:31,902
because of the mess the
Moravianos brought.

223
00:18:31,985 --> 00:18:33,779
The mess you all brought!

224
00:18:36,323 --> 00:18:38,117
I already gave Agent Alex

225
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:41,411
the most important information
that I have.

226
00:18:44,289 --> 00:18:47,626
I already revealed the true
identity of La Fornarina.

227
00:18:52,256 --> 00:18:53,257
Who?

228
00:18:58,262 --> 00:19:02,558
But it's none other than
the beloved of Pinagpala.

229
00:19:04,518 --> 00:19:05,519
Impossible.

230
00:19:07,521 --> 00:19:09,398
Too impossible. I won't believe that.

231
00:19:15,487 --> 00:19:17,739
You know what's impossible?

232
00:19:17,823 --> 00:19:22,744
For you to believe
that Mikoy is still your loyal asset.

233
00:19:24,621 --> 00:19:27,082
He's already tasted the Moraviano life.

234
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:28,458
He's fallen.

235
00:19:29,168 --> 00:19:30,502
Deeply fallen.

236
00:19:31,211 --> 00:19:34,798
Madly in love with the Valtrovi girl.

237
00:19:37,134 --> 00:19:38,260
Do you really think

238
00:19:38,343 --> 00:19:41,346
the information he's giving you
is still truthful?

239
00:19:42,806 --> 00:19:44,933
All of you are too naive

240
00:19:45,017 --> 00:19:48,353
if you think you can't be manipulated

241
00:19:48,437 --> 00:19:50,439
by Viktor and Chiara

242
00:19:50,522 --> 00:19:53,734
through your lover boy asset.

243
00:20:03,911 --> 00:20:05,078
Do you remember this?

244
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,540
We used to do this all the time in Prague.

245
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:26,266
Chiara?

246
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,517
Dear.

247
00:20:39,154 --> 00:20:39,988
Chiara.

248
00:20:47,913 --> 00:20:48,872
What happened?

249
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:05,180
My child.

250
00:21:10,269 --> 00:21:11,395
Child…

251
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:23,365
Who are you really?!

252
00:21:48,682 --> 00:21:49,683
My child.

253
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:56,606
Mama!

254
00:21:57,691 --> 00:21:58,692
Mom!

255
00:22:53,497 --> 00:22:56,249
Well, she managed to get some rest.

256
00:22:59,211 --> 00:23:01,296
Nothing. She's not saying anything.

257
00:23:02,672 --> 00:23:03,924
Nada.

258
00:23:04,883 --> 00:23:09,221
Whatever it is
all I know is she's deeply hurt.

259
00:23:15,393 --> 00:23:16,686
I don't know.

260
00:23:17,187 --> 00:23:18,563
I have no idea.

261
00:23:19,731 --> 00:23:22,025
The last time I saw her like this.

262
00:23:22,109 --> 00:23:22,984
Was when…

263
00:23:36,581 --> 00:23:37,958
Chiara, my child.

264
00:23:44,214 --> 00:23:45,048
Why?

265
00:24:07,404 --> 00:24:08,446
Bro!

266
00:24:11,533 --> 00:24:12,701
Are you okay?

267
00:24:13,702 --> 00:24:14,703
Did something happen?

268
00:24:17,497 --> 00:24:18,498
Mikoy.

269
00:24:19,291 --> 00:24:21,042
Angelito and I talked.

270
00:24:21,626 --> 00:24:25,422
We know you're the only asset
connected to G.A.G.O.

271
00:24:25,505 --> 00:24:27,090
But we think

272
00:24:27,174 --> 00:24:29,217
we can still help in many ways.

273
00:24:30,427 --> 00:24:34,806
Dad, let's talk about that some other day.

274
00:24:36,641 --> 00:24:38,602
I just want to be alone for now.

275
00:24:43,523 --> 00:24:44,691
We'll be here.

276
00:25:39,704 --> 00:25:40,789
<i>Why are you calling?</i>

277
00:25:40,872 --> 00:25:43,667
<i>Didn't you say</i>
<i>that I shouldn't answer this phone?</i>

278
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,085
<i>Mikoy, listen to me carefully.</i>

279
00:25:45,168 --> 00:25:46,544
<i>You need to stay away from Chiara.</i>

280
00:26:04,104 --> 00:26:05,605
<i>Stop closing your eyes to it.</i>

281
00:26:05,689 --> 00:26:08,733
The most dangerous Moraviano
is already right in front of you.

282
00:26:32,549 --> 00:26:33,967
You’re the one who has to stand down!

283
00:26:34,050 --> 00:26:35,260
Why don’t you try?

284
00:26:35,343 --> 00:26:37,637
Try to disarm me and we’ll see!

285
00:26:37,721 --> 00:26:38,555
You’re too…

286
00:26:38,638 --> 00:26:40,307
- What is happening here?!
- attached to Mikoy.

287
00:26:41,308 --> 00:26:43,643
Whatever this is Brusko, drop it.

288
00:26:46,646 --> 00:26:49,566
You’re hiding the truth from me.
So, let me remind you.
